---
import { getCollection, getEntry, render } from 'astro:content';
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroTitle from '~/components/HeroTitle.astro';
import PostCard from '~/components/PostCard.astro';
import DarkCTA from '~/components/DarkCTA.astro';
import SignupForm from '~/components/SignupForm.astro';
import FeaturedStory from '~/components/FeaturedStory.astro';
import XTimeline from '~/components/XTimeline.astro';
import Picture from '~/components/Picture.astro';
import { byDateDesc, entryHref, notDraft } from '~/lib/entries';
import { collectionPage } from '~/lib/seo';
import { link } from '~/lib/link';

const statement = await getEntry('page', 'home-statement');
const { Content: StatementBody } = await render(statement!);

const updates = (await getCollection('update'))
  .filter(notDraft)
  .sort(byDateDesc)
  .slice(0, 5);

const featured = updates[0];
const grid = updates.slice(1, 5);

const description = "The Aadhaar project, with its fundamental weaknesses and dangerous effects, continues to grow. Let's Rethink Aadhaar.";
const jsonLd = collectionPage({ name: 'Rethink Aadhaar', url: '/', description });
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Rethink Aadhaar"
  description={description}
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
  preloadImage="/media/1489594687018-VG8KQQP625TQFSNEP1FV-image-asset.jpeg"
>
  <HeroTitle align="center">Rethink<br/>Aadhaar</HeroTitle>

  <!-- Centred intro paragraph at a comfortable measure (~65ch). -->
  <div class="container-prose mt-10 md:mt-14 prose font-body text-pretty text-center mx-auto fade-up" style="max-width: 65ch;">
    <p>The Aadhaar project, to provide a unique number to all residents in India, was packaged as a welfare-enabling programme. It was sold as an initiative for greater inclusiveness in welfare, a tool against corruption, greater efficiency and so on.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Two-column block: canonical worn fingerprint hand image + serif paragraph. -->
  <section class="container-prose mt-16 md:mt-20 grid gap-8 md:gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 items-start fade-up delay-1">
    <figure class="m-0">
      <Picture
        src="/media/1489594687018-VG8KQQP625TQFSNEP1FV-image-asset.jpeg"
        alt="A worker's hand holding an Aadhaar enrolment slip — fingertips worn smooth from years of manual labour."
        width={1200}
        height={800}
        class="w-full h-auto block"
        avif
        eager
      />
    </figure>
    <div class="prose font-body text-pretty">
      <p>More than a decade later, evidence and testimony show the continuing destruction of welfare programmes due to their Aadhaar linkage. The Aadhaar project also presents the potential to enable mass surveillance, which threatens privacy and democratic practice.</p>
      <p>Indian residents and citizens have been lulled into believing that their privacy is the price they have to pay for better implementation of welfare programmes. In fact, the Aadhaar project threatens both our welfare, and right to privacy; and yet, even with its fundamental weaknesses and dangerous effects, it continues to grow.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-prose mt-20 md:mt-28 fade-up delay-1">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-3 text-center">Collective statement · 10 December 2025</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl text-balance leading-tight tracking-tight uppercase text-center">{statement!.data.title}</h2>
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert font-body mt-10 text-pretty mx-auto" style="max-width: 65ch;">
      <StatementBody />
    </div>
  </section>

  {featured && (
    <FeaturedStory href={entryHref('update', featured)} title={featured.data.title} date={featured.data.date}>
      {featured.data.excerpt && <p>{featured.data.excerpt}</p>}
    </FeaturedStory>
  )}

  <section class="container-prose mt-20 fade-up delay-2">
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-8">
      <h2 class="caps text-accent text-sm">Latest updates</h2>
      <a href={link('/blog')} class="caps text-xs hover:text-accent">All updates →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      {grid.map((u) => (
        <PostCard
          href={entryHref('update', u)}
          title={u.data.title}
          date={u.data.date}
          excerpt={u.data.excerpt}
          hero={u.data.hero}
        />
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <XTimeline />

  <section class="container-prose mt-20 md:mt-28 text-center fade-up">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-3">Get involved</p>
    <h2 class="hero-title text-balance">Let's rethink Aadhaar</h2>
    <SignupForm />
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-center gap-3">
      <DarkCTA href={link('/take-action')}>Take action now!</DarkCTA>
      <a href={link('/campaign2025')} class="btn-outline w-full sm:w-auto">Read Campaign 2025</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
